        "subject": "LU-11953 tests: conf-sanity cleanup",
        "message": "LU-11953 tests: conf-sanity cleanup\n\nMost conf-sanity tests assume cleanup has been run before\nthey start, but many tests also do not do this correctly on\nerror.\n\nRather than adding a stack_trap to almost every test, let's\nput cleanup() in $CLEANUP so it's run after every test.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic33631c1339b93c71d06701ccf0ae54a78816398\n"
      },
